ygData.subject: Starting Monster Guild
ygData.msgSnippet: Looking for more Troll and Ogre members to start up an official guild. The webpage is blackhand.packetloss.com We are looking to become the most organized mob
ygData.messageBody:
Looking for more Troll and Ogre members to start up an official guild.

The webpage is blackhand.packetloss.com

We are looking to become the most organized mob of monsters in
Bristlebane with focus on leveling through Dungeon/Exploration and
pickling Dwarves!

Want to know the way to Queynos from Innothule or the way to Neriak
from the Ferrott? Join us. We will equip your mind and character!
